        "content": "<p>I started porting <code>topology.basic</code> in <a href=\"https://github.com/leanprover-community/mathlib4/pull/1826\">!4#1826</a>, depends on <a href=\"https://github.com/leanprover-community/mathlib/pull/18288\">#18288</a></p>",
